a. Create the terraform user with admin permission
b. Create its Access Key (Access key ID and Secret Access Key)
c. On PowerShell locally, run
  $env:AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="AccessKeyID"
  $env:SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="SecretAccessKey"
  $env:AWS_DEFAULT_REGION="AWSRegion" (optional)
  
  
  In Linux/Mac
  export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="AccessKeyID"
  export SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="SecretAccessKey"
  export AWS_DEFAULT_REGION="AWSRegion" (optional)
  
Note: To be run every time you reload PowerShell or Terminal
